title: Works amazing! All features work great! Highly recommend!
text: I love it! Everything works! No password needed just Face ID and number verification great app to use if you forget passwords easy/need extra security for your Microsoft account. You can add infinite accounts and keep hackers out. Will continue to use for a LONG time. Thank you for this app, it’s a life saver.
